Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:11.53,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs16\alpha&H66&\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H0075EA&}ACG12调查小队【沉默似金_】抄自【F宅字幕组】\N仅供学习交流，禁止用于任何商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:04.18,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等着我...我一定会...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.18,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,呃 这是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:11.53,Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\an2}{\c&H6E3C42&}Re:{\c&H6E48B4&}小{\c&H317FB6&}剧场{\c&H060200&}之一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.51,Default - Top,Emilia,0,0,0,,好 快点回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:15.70,Default - Top,Subaru,0,0,0,,咦 这是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.05,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我记得好像是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:18.84,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,昴君你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,班会的铃声已经响了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.82,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我才想问怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:26.10,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,话说 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.51,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,什么做什么 班会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.86,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,我有好多要说的重要通知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.40,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等一下 艾米莉娅碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.43,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:37.18,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,用艾米莉娅碳这种奇怪的名称称呼老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:38.24,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,你真是个坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:41.08,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不是哪个啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:45.80,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,近日我因为十分尊敬老师您 才会在名字后边在上碳来着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:46.81,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:49.33,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,对对 就是这样 艾米莉娅碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:52.05,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,不好意思 我真是的 抱歉.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.32,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:53.32,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now, let's start over.\NUm, in homeroom today...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.47,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,我被困在什么魔法里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:57.01,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,{\an8}现在让我们开始吧  今天的班会是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:58.67,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,但是眼前的毫无疑问就是艾米莉娅碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.52,Default - italics,Subaru,0,0,0,,会被这种胡编乱造的谎言骗到的粗枝大叶的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:04.12,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,这种粗心大意用魔法是无法还原的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:04.12,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,Let's try to take care of our things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.95,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们来试着做些什么吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:09.45,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,对了帕克 如果是帕克的话说不定能知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.45,0:01:11.87,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,艾米莉娅碳 帕克 帕克在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:13.40,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:21.69,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,{\fs12\an7\3c&HFFB0D8&\b0}注:日语中的帕克发音和纸盒相同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:16.89,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,像牛奶之类的纸盒 因为是可再生材质
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:21.69,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,所以不可以扔进垃圾桶里 而是要好好丢进写有纸盒的可回收箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.34,0:01:21.69,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:23.28,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,啊 不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:26.72,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,可是纸盒的表面有经过防水加工
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:28.67,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,如果不分开丢弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.64,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,艾米莉娅碳实在是太博学了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:33.62,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,EMH 艾米莉娅碳超级博学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.49,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等等 这种话就先放到一边 我问的是帕克啊帕克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.44,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,对你来说重要得不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:39.60,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,重要的pakku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.97,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,美容面膜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:43.48,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,艾米莉娅碳就算不美容也已经足够可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:46.22,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,不是这个 是这种猫的样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:48.56,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,哦哦 我的画工好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:52.04,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,怎么了突然画了校长的肖像画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.11,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,校长是指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.31,Default,Puck,0,0,0,,我就是校长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.33,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,诶--？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.48,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:02.65,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,突然大叫妨碍课堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.95,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,老师要怄气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.49,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,怄气这个说法近年真是没怎么听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:08.93,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,我已经生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.13,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,昴君 去走廊罚站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:12.27,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.17,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:15.27,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:18.50,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:22.02,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,我一定会 回到原来的世界..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:25.52,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,1018)}话说这种情况下 原来的世界到底指的是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:28.60,Default,Emilia,0,0,0,,昴君刚才因为贫血晕倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:30.17,Default,Subaru,0,0,0,,呃 那个是贫血吗
